FBIS3-2016 "drchi043_h_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 West Europe Cooperation With Airbus Industrie Enhanced OW0403025694 Beijing XINHUA in English 0158 GMT 4 Mar 94 OW0403025694 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Shanghai, March 4 (XINHUA) -- China Eastern Airlines will this year buy four airbuses from the Airbus Industrie of Europe, according to official sources. China Northern Airlines and Northwestern Airlines have also ordered five airbuses from the company, according to a press conference held here Tuesday [2 March] by the company. Officials of the company in charge of China affairs said that the company plans to set up a training center in Beijing, to train professional pilots for China. The company and the China aviation suppliers corporation several days ago signed a co-operative pact under which some departments of the China aviation industry will produce spare parts for the company, official sources said.
